@startuml TR4D3RZ_MVP_Demo_State_Diagram
!theme plain

title TR4D3RZ MVP Demo - Node State Machine

[*] --> Disconnected

state "Disconnected" as Disconnected {
    Disconnected : No MQTT connection
    Disconnected : Waiting for startup
}

state "Connecting" as Connecting {
    Connecting : MQTT CONNECT sent
    Connecting : Awaiting CONNACK
}

state "Booting" as Booting {
    Booting : Connected to broker
    Booting : Initializing subsystems
    Booting : Publishing initial status
}

state "Ready" as Ready {
    Ready : Fully operational
    Ready : Processing messages
    Ready : Publishing heartbeats
}

state "Degraded" as Degraded {
    Degraded : Partial functionality
    Degraded : Some subsystems offline
    Degraded : Still connected to broker
}

state "Offline" as Offline {
    Offline : Connection lost
    Offline : Attempting reconnect
}

Disconnected --> Connecting : start()
Connecting --> Booting : CONNACK received
Connecting --> Offline : Connection timeout
Booting --> Ready : Initialization complete
Booting --> Degraded : Subsystem failure
Ready --> Degraded : Error detected
Ready --> Offline : Connection lost
Degraded --> Ready : Recovery complete
Degraded --> Offline : Connection lost
Offline --> Connecting : Reconnect attempt
Offline --> [*] : stop()

note right of Ready
  **Ready State Activities**:
  • Publish heartbeat every 5s
  • Process incoming messages
  • Generate events (simulators)
  • Update UI (observatory)
end note

note right of Degraded
  **Degraded Triggers**:
  • Message publish failure
  • Subscription loss
  • Simulator error
  • High message latency
end note

@enduml
